export interface ITimebookProps { startDay: Date } export const TimeBook = (props: ITimebookProps) => { const hourData = { 'M': 4.5, 'T': 3.0, } function addDays(date: Date, days: number) { let result: Date = date result.setDate(result.getDate() + days) return result } const endDay = addDays(props.startDay, 6) return <>

From {props.startDay.toDateString()} until {endDay.toDateString()}

M T W Th F S Su
{hourData['M']} {hourData['T']}
}
